  "texts": [
    "In this way, these methods can process efficiently high-dimensional and spatially sparse data.",
    "Semantic segmentation-Point-based methodsPoint-based networks operate on unstructured point clouds, avoiding some limitations posed by previous methods, such as projection and discretization.",
    "In this category, point cloud data processing is conducted directly.",
    "These methods are divided into point-wise MLP, point convolution, RNN based, and graph-based methods.Point-wise MLP methods utilize the joint MLP as the main unit of their network due to its superior effectiveness.",
    "However, the extracted features by these methods may not fully describe the local geometry and common interactions between points."
  ]
